<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Account Deletion | Smana Hotels</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --gold: #b8965a;
      --gold-light: #d4b07a;
      --dark: #1a1612;
      --warm: #2c2520;
      --cream: #f5f0e8;
      --text: #3a3028;
      --muted: #7a6e64;
      --border: #e0d5c5;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      background: var(--dark);
      padding: 24px 48px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* Hero band */
    .hero-band {
      background: var(--warm);
      padding: 60px 48px 52px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #3a3028;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-band::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 50% 120%, rgba(184,150,90,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-band .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .hero-band h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .hero-band p {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #b0a698;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Main content */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 56px 32px 80px;
    }

    /* Notice box */
    .notice {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .notice-icon {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 1px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .notice p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .notice p strong {
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Section titles */
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .section-label::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .section-intro {
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    /* Steps */
    .steps {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 28px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both;
    }

    .step:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .step:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
    .step:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .step:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
    .step:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .step:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }

    .step-num {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      min-width: 34px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .step-body h3 {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .step-body p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .step-body .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f0ebe0;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', monospace;
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 2px 9px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* Alternative method */
    .alt-method {
      background: var(--dark);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 32px 36px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .alt-method::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30px; right: -30px;
      width: 140px; height: 140px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(184,150,90,0.08);
    }

    .alt-method .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
    .alt-method .section-label::after { background: rgba(184,150,90,0.25); }

    .alt-method h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }

    .alt-method p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #b0a698;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .email-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 11px 22px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .email-link:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

    /* Data info */
    .data-info {
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .data-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .data-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      header { padding: 18px 24px; }
      main { padding: 40px 20px 60px; }
      .hero-band { padding: 48px 24px 40px; }
      .alt-method { padding: 24px 22px; }
    }

    .data-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
    }

    .data-card .label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .data-card p {
      font-size: 0.87rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: var(--dark);
      padding: 28px 48px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #5a5048;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a href="https://smanahotels.com" class="logo">Smana <span>Hotels</span></a>
</header>

<div class="hero-band">
  <div class="eyebrow">Account Management</div>
  <h1>Account Deletion Request</h1>
  <p>Follow the steps below to permanently delete your Smana Hotels account and all associated personal data.</p>
</div>

<main>

  <div class="notice">
    <div class="notice-icon">⚠️</div>
    <p><strong>Please note:</strong> Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. All your bookings history, saved preferences, and loyalty points will be removed. If you have any upcoming reservations, please ensure they are cancelled or completed before requesting deletion.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- In-App Steps -->
  <div class="section-label">Option 1 — In-App</div>
  <h2>Delete via the App</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">The quickest way to delete your account is directly from within the Smana Hotels app.</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Open the Smana Hotels App</h3>
        <p>Launch the app on your device and make sure you are signed in to the account you wish to delete.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Go to Profile</h3>
        <p>Tap the <strong>Profile</strong> or <strong>Account</strong> icon, usually found in the bottom navigation bar or the top-right corner of the home screen.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Open Settings</h3>
        <p>Inside your profile, tap <strong>Settings</strong> or the gear icon to access account preferences.</p>
        <span class="tag">Profile → Settings</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Select "Delete Account"</h3>
        <p>Scroll to the bottom of the Settings page and tap <strong>Delete Account</strong>. You may be asked to confirm your password.</p>
        <span class="tag">Settings → Delete Account</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">5</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Confirm Deletion</h3>
        <p>Read the confirmation message carefully, then tap <strong>Confirm Delete</strong> to permanently remove your account. You will receive a confirmation email once the process is complete.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Email method -->
  <div class="alt-method">
    <div class="section-label">Option 2 — Via Email</div>
    <h2>Request by Email</h2>
    <p>If you are unable to access the app or prefer to request deletion manually, send us an email from the address linked to your account. We will process your request within <strong style="color:#d4b07a">7 business days</strong> and send you a confirmation once complete.</p>
    <a href="mailto:privacy@smanahotels.com?subject=Account%20Deletion%20Request&body=Hello%2C%0A%0AI%20would%20like%20to%20request%20the%20permanent%20deletion%20of%20my%20Smana%20Hotels%20account.%0A%0ARegistered%20email%3A%20%5Byour%20email%5D%0AFull%20name%3A%20%5Byour%20name%5D%0A%0APlease%20confirm%20once%20my%20account%20has%20been%20deleted.%0A%0AThank%20you." class="email-link">
      ✉ &nbsp;Email a Deletion Request
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Data info -->
  <div class="data-info">
    <div class="section-label">What gets deleted</div>
    <h2>Your Data & What Happens to It</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">We take your privacy seriously. Here is what happens to your data when you request account deletion.</p>

    <div class="data-grid">
      <div class="data-card">
        <div class="label">Deleted Immediately</div>
        <p>Personal profile information, saved payment methods, preferences, loyalty points, and login credentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="data-card">
        <div class="label">Deleted within 30 Days</div>
        <p>Booking history, communications, and any remaining app activity logs associated with your account.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="data-card">
        <div class="label">Retained for Legal Purposes</div>
        <p>Transaction records may be retained for up to 7 years as required by financial and tax regulations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="data-card">
        <div class="label">Need Help?</div>
        <p>For any questions about your data, contact our support team at <a href="mailto:privacy@smanahotels.com" style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none;">privacy@smanahotels.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<footer>
  <p>
    &copy; 2025 Smana Hotels. All rights reserved. &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <a href="https://smanahotels.com/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <a href="https://smanahotels.com">Back to Website</a>
  </p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
